</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex>H  \colon  f  \sim   1_{ A }</fr:tex> be a <fr:link
href="erct-0014.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-0014">homotopy</fr:link> from <fr:tex>f \colon  A  \to  A</fr:tex> onto the identity function. Then we may construct a higher homotopy from <fr:tex>H \circ  f</fr:tex> to <fr:tex>\mathsf {act}_{ f } \circ  H</fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
